Before making changes, read:
- `docs/SESSION_HANDOFF.md` — machine handoff, architecture state, recent work
- `docs/AI_CONTEXT.md` — product rules, frozen UI foundation
- `EVENT_TAXONOMY.md` — analytics events (never use magic strings)

Hard rules:
- Features use `AnalyticsService` only — never import PostHog or Clarity directly
- All analytics via `AppEvent.*` from `@/core/analytics/events`
- Chits are standalone entities — not loans
- UI Foundation V1.0 is frozen — no redesign unless explicitly asked
- No git commits unless the user requests them
- Minimize scope; match existing code conventions
